For more details or assistance, Triton Middle School can be contacted at (507) 418-7510.

In the beautiful city of Dodge Center, Triton Middle School is celebrated for creating a dynamic learning environment that champions diversity and promotes a sense of belonging among all students. Its efforts to tailor educational experiences to the needs of a varied student body significantly enhance the educational landscape in Minnesota, equipping learners with the skills necessary to thrive in a globally interconnected world.
